data.description: **THIS home qualifies  for a lower interest rate, ask agent for more details**Move-in ready meets home sweet home.  You don't want to miss this three bedroom home just half a mile from HPU.  Nestle by the fireplace in this warm and inviting home with hardwood floors throughout.  Open kitchen and dining room makes for a welcoming area for cooking and entertaining.  The first floor has two spacious bedrooms, wide hallway and a full bathroom.  The second floor is a primary suite retreat with a beautiful brick chimney accent adorning the room and an ensuite full bathroom.  Additional features include an updated kitchen with SS appliances, new roof, new front door, all updated light fixtures, new gas furnace and a fenced in backyard.  All kitchen appliances remain.
